src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab324b0eb7a39071f0c6af969d1cb7ebb45b49c","tid":3863,"uid":18246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:02:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>社工係用社會提供既外界資源去幫助人<br />\n而心理輔導係透過rebuild人既內心力量去幫助人<br />\n社工當然亦會學到輔導技巧，但唔夠深入同全面</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n社工都會rebuild人既內心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個人覺得社工就broad啲 包埋counseling <br />\n而心理輔導就單向啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n純粹個人感覺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗心理輔導比較micro d, <br />\n社工偏向會搵埋案主身邊既資源 比如屋企人果啲<br />\n同埋個人覺得社工重視幫人既哲學多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 只係讀社工既小薯仔"},{"pid":"3221352779279f3d9ac71b7e7fd991add5463434","tid":3863,"uid":24554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:07:14.000Z","msg":"應該係心理輔導？<br />\n因為佢真係可以好specific咁搵到你諗野既方向/路徑<br />\n然後引導你或者講番一啲你一直無為意 自己有既思想謬誤<br />\n好似真係會比較有針對性咁"},{"pid":"8821c3fc4a0a07045e8278a6e03b3a2b9d575c21","tid":3863,"uid":10317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:36:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>社工定心理輔導算係專科</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港現況：<br />\n社工有牌，唔係個個可以做<br />\n輔導無牌，咩人都可以叫自己做輔導員，有人信就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcca02aad86c2d60ddb87ade6009063d7053b3e4","tid":3863,"uid":43067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:11:17.000Z","msg":"好有錢又唔擔心收入少就讀輔導"},{"pid":"64b24b5624a17e8713b9f0e3c1c3705998b78df2","tid":3863,"uid":24131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:33:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>社工定心理輔導算係專科</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港現況：<br />\n社工有牌，唔係個個可以做<br />\n輔導無牌，咩人都可以叫自己做輔導員，有人信就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過心理學家都無牌wo"},{"pid":"a332b7515db35ec3a59ec885f2e37cd63442d452","tid":3863,"uid":24131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:15:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好有錢又唔擔心收入少就讀輔導</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  香港人樓都買唔起 邊會有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8257774d7e5cb557e87c6835185ea77d192391d","tid":3863,"uid":11483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:26:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"01c848f1c609d8e63b1ab1d5e0a870f341bff3b1","tid":3863,"uid":24131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:55:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港現況：<br />\n社工有牌，唔係個個可以做<br />\n輔導無牌，咩人都可以叫自己做輔導員，有人信就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過心理學家都無牌wo</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽過CP未</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ncp 係香港都係得self-regulation <br />\n而家cp or edu psy 都無政府立法強制注冊制度 任何人都可以話自己係心理學家"},{"pid":"f60a848fbd037b9dc115dc534aa33bb83b7280d0","tid":3863,"uid":44647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:03:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過心理學家都無牌wo</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽過CP未</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ncp 係香港都係得self-regulation <br />\n而家cp or edu psy 都無政府立法強制注冊制度 任何人都可以話自己係心理學家</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCp 已經約定俗成左<br />\n仲有力過社工果d so called 立法註冊制度<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同社工比不可吳日言語喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3a288ae36e753b03a281f762f78deb6f772232","tid":3863,"uid":67901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:19:22.000Z","msg":"如果你話輔導一定係輔導員 <br />\n以我所知社工係主要負責r福利 幫人解決燃眉之急/做social justice <br />\n雖則輔導員都有social justice嘅概念(但當然好理想化) 但最主要都係由心理學入手 訓練佢地輔導技巧<br />\n所以如果科黎講一定係心理輔導<br />\n無牌真係個好大嘅問題 以我所知心理學會dcop都可以睇到會員名單 有協會係盡力咁去認證翻輔導員<br />\n其實好多人都爭取緊個牌照制度 但香港從來都無在意過輔導員 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以如果去心理輔導 你都要有打算係同好多人一樣爭取輔導員地位"},{"pid":"d7de7490b1ea46e4aae5ad28053677122bc7bfaf","tid":3863,"uid":24131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:19:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽過CP未</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ncp 係香港都係得self-regulation <br />\n而家cp or edu psy 都無政府立法強制注冊制度 任何人都可以話自己係心理學家</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCp 已經約定俗成左<br />\n仲有力過社工果d so called 立法註冊制度<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同社工比不可吳日言語喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你啱 <br />\ncp 當然有力過社工 大學爆gpa都未必入到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過唔係私人clinic開果d 邊個知果d 咩人<br />\n<br />\nbtw city scope 之前都有開cp doc prgram<br />\n,<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/van/htm/News/20141027/HK-gfa1_r.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2Fvan%2Fhtm%2FNews%2F20141027%2FHK-gfa1_r.htm&d=eSihygRt4ZE%2FMn2LPEVkfsW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=ef72d6ea\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mingpaocanada.com/van/htm/News/20141027/HK-gfa1_r.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7c4180fda10c6a899395e4c3db73be60a68a49e3","tid":3863,"uid":24131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:23:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你話輔導一定係輔導員 <br />\n以我所知社工係主要負責r福利 幫人解決燃眉之急/做social justice <br />\n雖則輔導員都有social justice嘅概念(但當然好理想化) 但最主要都係由心理學入手 訓練佢地輔導技巧<br />\n所以如果科黎講一定係心理輔導<br />\n無牌真係個好大嘅問題 以我所知心理學會dcop都可以睇到會員名單 有協會係盡力咁去認證翻輔導員<br />\n其實好多人都爭取緊個牌照制度 但香港從來都無在意過輔導員 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以如果去心理輔導 你都要有打算係同好多人一樣爭取輔導員地位</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點爭取 連coun psy  self-regulation 都未有 輔導員係香港應該等到2046<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffd3df1a06a7450234b0b7c5b7426631c9aa3d75","tid":3863,"uid":24131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:26:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你話輔導一定係輔導員 <br />\n以我所知社工係主要負責r福利 幫人解決燃眉之急/做social justice <br />\n雖則輔導員都有social justice嘅概念(但當然好理想化) 但最主要都係由心理學入手 訓練佢地輔導技巧<br />\n所以如果科黎講一定係心理輔導<br />\n無牌真係個好大嘅問題 以我所知心理學會dcop都可以睇到會員名單 有協會係盡力咁去認證翻輔導員<br />\n其實好多人都爭取緊個牌照制度 但香港從來都無在意過輔導員 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以如果去心理輔導 你都要有打算係同好多人一樣爭取輔導員地位</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而且香港政府點會做野 連營養師香港自己都無注冊制度 要靠外國做注冊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97182ed82af0f06bc47bc1a5042b54dd53ca0e1","tid":3863,"uid":24131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T12:03:46.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd803b18f2c789999517a255552bd698a13e5082","tid":3863,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:19:00.000Z","msg":"心理治療師<br />\n<br />\n不過好撚貴"}]}